<ab facs="#facs_71_r2l28">wır von <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>erſamk<ex>eit</ex></expan> ein <expan>ſund<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>wolgefall<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> Alſo tun wır <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>wırdık<ex>eit</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_71_r2l29">ʒu <expan>wıſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> daʒ vns fürbracht wırdt / Daʒ <expan>ſölıch<ex>er</ex></expan> eẅr fleıſſ vnd gute <expan>meynu<ex>n</ex>g</expan> noch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_71_r2l30"><expan>vnu<ex>er</ex>fenklıch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ſey daʒ <expan>derſ<ex>elb</ex></expan> Conuent <expan>ſölıch<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>redlıch<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>gut<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>ordnu<ex>n</ex>g</expan> als ſıe vor </ab>
